title: NFL ATL: 'CJ2K' recap; AFC North Roster Reset
itunes:title: NFL ATL: 'CJ2K' recap; AFC North Roster Reset
description:
A room full of heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Marc Sessler and Chris Wesseling -- picks apart the Chris Johnson signing, breaking down how he’ll fare for the New York Jets.  Elsewhere, the gang checks out the penultimate division in its “Roster Reset” series, heading this time to the very tight AFC North.
